data.description: Welcome to this charming residence nestled in the heart of an equestrian neighborhood. Situated on a corner lot, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort, functionality, & elegance. As you approach, you'll be greeted by a rocking chair front porch. Step inside where you'll discover ample space for family & guests alike. The main level beckons with spacious dining room, perfect for hosting intimate dinners or festive gatherings. Den/office offers a retreat for work or relaxation. Great Room has windows will bathe the space w/ natural light & has a gas fireplace & built in bookcases. Well-appointed kitchen w/ ample counterspace & cabinets plus large breakfast area. Step from kitchen onto screened porch overlooking private fenced in backyard. Access to rear loading garage also from kitchen. Bedrooms are upstairs w/ a 5th bedroom slash bonus room. HOA covers pool, tennis courts & playgrounds.  There is a barn in neighborhood for your horses with a separate fee for boarding.
